      <title>WeWork 與債權人達成和解，拒絕諾依曼的收購要約</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wework-reaches-settlement-with-creditors-rebuffs-neumann-bid-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共享辦公空間提供商 WeWork 週一宣布與其初級債權人達成和解，並從高級債權人處獲得新的現金注入，推進破產協議，該協議拒絕了聯合創始人兼前所有者 Adam Neumann 提出的 6.5 億美元報價。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wework-reaches-settlement-with-creditors-rebuffs-neumann-bid-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 19:25:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
